'''Mehmet <U+00C7>ak<U+0131>r''' (born [[January 4]], [[1984]] in [[Bala, Ankara|Bala]], [[Turkey]]) is a [[Turkish people|Turkish]] [[football (soccer)|football]] player. He currently plays [[attacking midfielder]] for [[Gen<U+00E7>lerbirli<U+011F>i]] in the [[Turkcell Super League]].

